Seven people have been killed in a car crash on Umgeni Road in Durban this morning. eNCA's Dasen Thathiah is at the scene. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - Seven people have been killed in a car crash on the N2 highway near Umgeni road in KwaZulu-Natal. One person was seriously injured and has been rushed to hospital. READ:Â Six injured in Durban crash The deceased and one survivor were trapped in the car, forcing officials to use the jaws of life. No other vehicles appear to have been involved. Police are investigating the cause of the crash.